line_1: THE famous old Prophet that twenty years toil'd,
line_2: To write us the Psalms that dunce Hopkins has spoil'd,

line_1: For which thy anxious fathers toil'd,
line_2: Thy white and even thread has spoil'd:

line_1: Wi' a sigh were relating how hard they had toil'd;
line_2: Twa vet'rans grown gray, wi' their muskets sair soil'd,
